<A HREF="arcane.php3"><B>Hall of Arcane Sciences:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ARIEL">
Finally, after a year or more, we are revamping our Arcane Spells area! Originally I started them out as simple html pages, but they were not very easy to update or add too, so finally Sorontar made a new database version to replace them.<BR><BR>
In our new <A HREF="arcane.php3">Arcane</A> section you will find every spell in EverQuest, along with detailed notes on their uses, advantages, disadvantages, hints, tips, etc. All searchable by level and class.<BR><BR>
At the moment we have all the songs inputted for Bards, and I am in the middle of inputing the Wizard's spells. As there are well over 1000 spells in EverQuest, it may be a week or two until they all get listed, so check back frequently. I will be inputting data class by class.
</FONT><BR><BR>


